author = "Antonio Aguilera and Rocío Trastoy and Francisco Rodríguez-Frias and Juan Luis Muñoz-Bellido and Santiago Melón and Adelina Suárez and Antonio Orduña and Isabel Viciana and Bernal S. Samuel and Silvia García-Bujalance and Natalia Montiel and José Manuel Molina and Miren Basaras and Felipe Fernández-Cuenca and Isabel García-Arata and Gabriel Reina and María Dolores Ocete and Ana Fuentes and Daniel Navarro {de la Cruz} and Leonardo Nieto and Ana Blázquez {de Castro} and María Buti and Marta Álvarez and Federico García",
